      <title>交易员等待英伟达：市场休整，亚洲股市涨跌互现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/asian-stocks-look-mixed-as-traders-await-nvidia-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[继华尔街谨慎交易之后，亚洲股市将迎来无精打采的一天，交易员们热切等待周三英伟达公司的财报，该公司是推动牛市的人工智能狂热的核心芯片制造商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/asian-stocks-look-mixed-as-traders-await-nvidia-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 22:34:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关键证人称，“土拨鼠日”交易给Archegos带来了风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/-groundhog-day-trading-built-risk-at-archegos-key-witness-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Archegos Capital Management 创始人 Bill Hwang 决定进行交易后，他又做了一次。然后再次。然后再次。高级员工的反应是用“土拨鼠日快乐”互相问候，这是对比尔·默里经典循环喜剧的致敬。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/-groundhog-day-trading-built-risk-at-archegos-key-witness-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 21:41:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
