      <title>Soroban Capital 与 Elliott 一起增持江森自控股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/soroban-capital-amasses-johnson-controls-stake-alongside-elliott</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，索罗班资本合伙公司(Soroban Capital Partners)已持有工业公司江森自控国际公司(Johnson Controls International Plc)的大量股份，这加剧了激进投资者埃利奥特投资管理公司(Elliott Investment Management)带来的压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/soroban-capital-amasses-johnson-controls-stake-alongside-elliott</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 19:25:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
